        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Make sure you can get yourself out of a sticky situation with the ASR Tactical Escape & Evasion Saws!<br><br>This 4 pack of saws comes with 2 diamond grit and 2 tungsten carbide saws, which will cut through most metals and even glass. Each saw is about 3\" in length, making it small enough to keep in discrete locations without being noticed. <br><br>These saws are thin, covert and lightweight. We've included a safe storage container to keep them all packaged together until you need to deploy them. Don't get caught in a bad situation without this set of escape saws!<br><br><br><br><b>Package Includes:</b><br>-(2) Diamond Grit Escape Saws<br>-(2) Tungsten Carbide Escape Saws",
